      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95">
        各市区町村の詳細な調査レポートで、最適な住居選択をお手伝いします
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/ja/services/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-yellow-400 text-cyan-900 font-bold text-lg rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all duration-300"
        >
